# ============================================================
# TicketBox Concert Public API Test Requests
# Use the "REST Client" extension in VS Code to run these.
# ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### 1. List Concerts (Default page=0, size=10)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/concerts
Accept: application/json

### 2. List Concerts (With Pagination - page 0, size 5)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/concerts?page=0&size=5
Accept: application/json

### 3. Get Concert Detail (Anh Trai Say Hi)
# Replace the UUID with any real ID from the list response if needed
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/concerts/11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111
Accept: application/json

### 4. Get Concert Detail (Sơn Tùng M-TP)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/concerts/22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222
Accept: application/json

### 5. Get Concert Detail (404 - Not Found)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/concerts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json
